items.name: Simply Comfy
items.description:
This is just an ULTRA simple ComfyUI workflow. It only has the Checkpoint, two Lora slots, and the positive and negative prompt zones. This is for people who are new to ComfyUI or just want something super fast and simple.

This workflow is for checkpoints that don't need a refiner such as SD 1.5 checkpoints as well as the many new SDXL models that don't require refiners.

You'll get an error message at first I'm sure as your checkpoints and loras will be in a different location than mine. Once you switch out the checkpoint and loras you should be good to go!

EDIT: This was my first ComfyUi workflow, I have a couple more up that, while slightly more complex, are more fun to work with. I encourage you to check them out and give them a spin! 😀

items.name: 【再世】next life-戎祥
items.description:
这是群星再世第七十三期，以后会不定期出去世的群星Lora，以纪念他们。

戎祥被大陆观众熟知，是在《疯狂的赛车》里饰演乌龙帮老大“东海”，又凶狠又自带搞笑成分，其他的影视作品角色也大多都是这一类型，三十多年前，戎祥的演艺生涯源于齐秦。因为他早期一直是在做齐秦的助理，或许在演艺圈受到了艺术氛围的感染，他在1991年的齐秦演唱会上正式宣布进入演艺圈。出道之初的戎祥一直制作各综艺节目，同时还是胡瓜的助理，慢慢的获得了“台湾综艺大哥”的称号。

戎祥第一次出演的作品是1995年在李修贤、张家辉主演动作片《特警急先锋》客串，虽然只是一个小配角，却将他从幕后推向了观众。后来，他在神话历史剧《布袋和尚》扮演“国师”。在这两部作品之后，戎祥又重心转移到综艺，十余年间再没有作品，综艺节目《综艺万花筒》《百战百胜》《红白胜利》《金曲龙虎榜》《欢喜玉玲珑》等均有他的主持或客串演出。也曾自组“胖子乐团”、“红孩儿乐团”、“Mr.Big乐团”，《疯狂的赛车》闽南语主题曲《浮沉的兄弟》也是由戎祥演唱。

国有国法，家有家规，本地帮会太没有礼貌了！

2013年，因酗酒突发心肌梗塞去世，享年44岁。

https://t.me/+Vm8qxYr2QYgxMjJl 我的群组

items.name: CG architecture(古建筑）
items.description:
这是一个中国风建筑模型

这次的V2版本，调整了策略，单独以单体东方建筑训练，通过控制权重比例来实现场景里的建筑比例

所以说这个模型既可以生成俯视角度的单体建筑游戏资源，也可以控制比例权重生成中国风格的场景插画

生成游戏单体建筑资源的时候，要把负面关键词中灰色，单色类的词语去掉，因为游戏资源背景就是灰色，不然会污染背景

生成场景插画的时候负面词正常输入就行，不过要控制lora比例权重

单体建筑触发关键词：俯视角度，静物，东亚建筑

单体建筑举例：东亚建筑， 顶视图， 没有人， 灰色背景， 简单的背景， 风景， 楼梯， 建筑，柱子，静物

负面词：（最差质量：2），（低质量：2），（正常质量：2），低分辨率，正常质量

场景插画举例：风景， 树， 天空， 建筑， 东亚建筑， 户外， 没有人， 云彩， 天， 水， 反射， 建造， 池塘， 河， 桥， 草

负面词：（最差质量：2）、（低质量：2）、（正常质量：2）、低分辨率、正常质量、（（单色））、（（灰度））

画布尺寸：768x768 开启高清放大：R-ESRGAN 4x+

微信模型定制合作：yangzhenyu7849

作者b站个人用户：https://space.bilibili.com/403361177?spm id from=333.999.0.0

This is a model of Chinese-style architecture

This V2 version, the strategy is adjusted, and the single oriental building training is used separately, and the building proportion in the scene is realized by controlling the weight ratio

Therefore, this model can not only generate a single building game asset with a top-down view, but also control the proportional weight to generate Chinese-style scene illustrations

When generating game single building resources, remove gray and monochrome words from negative keywords, because the background of game resources is gray, otherwise it will pollute the background

When generating scene illustrations, negative words can be entered normally, but the LORA proportional weight should be controlled

Individual buildings trigger keywords: top-down view, still life, East Asian architecture

Examples of single buildings: East Asian architecture, top view, no people, gray background, simple background, landscape, stairs, architecture, columns, still lifes

Negative words: (worst quality: 2), (low quality: 2), (normal quality: 2), low resolution, normal quality

Scene illustration example: landscape, tree, sky, architecture, East Asian architecture, outdoors, no man, cloud, sky, water, reflection, building, pond, river, bridge, grass

Negative words: (worst quality: 2), (low quality: 2), (normal quality: 2), low resolution, normal quality, ((monochrome), ((grayscale))

items.name: MysteriousEasternpower（中国风游戏角色）
items.description:
首次炼制大模型，经历了多次弯路，最终找到方向，练出了纯粹的中国风大模型

炼制二次元和写实风格的模型比较容易，炼制中国风格的模型有几个难点，关键词不好形容，中国的元素很多都是意象化的，有很深的文化内涵，AI理解不了，就得反复调整关键词反复打磨，训练集也调整了很久

这次炼制的是实用化的专项模型，属于2d风格中国风模型

大模型名称定为MysteriousEasternpower（意思为神秘的东方力量）

专门用于出 角色立绘：（触发关键词后缀）游戏角色,美术设计，全身，原创艺术设计 触发效果

搭配的几个lora模型分为（均已上传）

Peking Opera京剧风格：艺术家，中国戏剧服装，京剧 （触发关键词）

CG illustration游戏美宣（插画）：游戏插画，游戏艺术，中国古代风格 （触发关键词）

Ancient architecture古建筑：中国建筑，场景，东亚建筑设计（触发关键词）

Antique residence古民居（室内）：中式房屋，古建筑设计，室内（触发关键词）

游戏角色立绘虽然可以生成出来，但是不是完美的，众说周知AI没有设计能力，会存在设计bug，逻辑不通，手脚结构变形，不合理的地方手绘去修改就行了

作者本人B站用户账号：鸡肉爱土豆

网址：https://space.bilibili.com/403361177?spm_id

The first time refining a large model, after many detours, finally found the direction and practiced a pure Chinese style model

Refining two-dimensional and realistic style models is relatively easy, refining Chinese style models has several difficulties, keywords are not easy to describe, many Chinese elements are imagery, there is a deep cultural connotation, AI can not understand, you have to repeatedly adjust the keywords and polish repeatedly, the training set has also been adjusted for a long time

This time it is a practical special model, which belongs to the 2D style Chinese style model

The name of the large model is Mysterious Easternpower (meaning mysterious eastern power)

Dedicated to character standing drawing: (trigger keyword suffix) game character, art design, full body, original art design trigger effect

The LoRa model is divided into:

Peking Opera style: (trigger keywords) artist, Chinese theater costume, Peking Opera

Game Meixuan (illustration) :(trigger keywords) game illustration, game art, ancient Chinese style

Ancient architecture: (trigger keywords) Chinese architecture, scenes, East Asian architectural design

Ancient Folk House (Interior) :(trigger keywords) Chinese House, Ancient Architectural Design, Interior

Although the game character standing drawing can be generated, but it is not perfect, it is said that the AI has no design ability, there will be design bugs, logic does not make sense, hand and foot structure deformation, unreasonable places to draw by hand to modify

  • yuuki mikan: yuuki mikan, hair bobbles, additional prompts: topknot

  • momo:momo, hair flowers, additional prompts: tail, demon tail

items.name: Amédée Ozenfant for SDXL
items.description:
About the artist:

[From Wikipedia]

Amédée Ozenfant (15 April 1886 – 4 May 1966) was a French cubist painter and writer. Together with Charles-Edouard Jeanneret (later known as Le Corbusier) he founded the Purist movement.

Amédée Ozenfant was one of the lesser-known cubism artist in modern French art history. However, he was influencial in shaping the way of modernism architecture together with Le Corbusier (father of modernism architecture).

The value of his artwork, expeicially his oil paintings with regard to still life objects (vase, glasses, tables guitars etc), lies on the fact that it directly established the aesthetic value of purism (together with Le Corbusier's artworks), which is the conceptual foundation behind mordenism architecture.

  • No more SDXL refiner model required to further improve the image quality;

  • Best to use 1024x1024 or higher resolution;

Further info or colab:

I'm happy to receive constructive feedbacks from anyone who's interested in artistic styles and concepts from established artists (either contemporary or past).

You are welcomed to contact me via the following ways:

Milica Bogdanovna Jovovich[ (born December 17, 1975), known professionally as Milla Jovovich (MEE-lə), is an American actress and model. Her starring roles in numerous science-fiction and action films led the music channel VH1 to deem her the "reigning queen of kick-butt" in 2006. In 2004, Forbes determined that she was the highest-paid model in the world.

Born in Kiev and raised in Los Angeles, Jovovich began modeling when Herb Ritts photographed her for the cover of the Italian magazine Lei in 1987. Richard Avedon featured her in Revlon's "Most Unforgettable Women in the World" advertisements. In 1988, Jovovich made her screen debut in the television film The Night Train to Kathmandu and appeared in her first feature film, Two Moon Junction.

Jovovich gained attention for her role in the 1991 romance film Return to the Blue Lagoon, as she was 15 years old at the time. She was considered to have a breakthrough with her role in the 1997 French science-fiction action film The Fifth Element, written and directed by Luc Besson. She and Besson married that year, but soon divorced. She starred as the heroine and martyr in Besson's The Messenger: The Story of Joan of Arc (1999). From 2002 to 2016, Jovovich portrayed Alice in the action horror film franchise Resident Evil, which became the highest-grossing film series to be based on video games.

Jovovich released a debut album, The Divine Comedy, in 1994, and a follow-up, The People Tree Sessions, in 1998. She continues to release demos for other songs on her official website and frequently contributes to film soundtracks. In 2003, model Carmen Hawk and she created the clothing line Jovovich–Hawk, which ran until 2008. Jovovich has her own production company, Creature Entertainment.

items.name: OyariAshito - Artist Style
items.description:
OyariAshito - Artist Style

This LoRA is trained based on the art style of OyariAshito(大槍葦人).

v1.0 is trained on works from 2002 to 2007.

v1.1 is trained on works from 2007 to 2014.

v1.0 carries a soft and ephemeral atmosphere, characterized by expressions that make the most of pencil lines. There's a tendency for the outlines to be bold and emphasized.

v1.1 edges slightly closer to a latest style, with outlines generally becoming finer. Moreover, it excels in generating mature female.

The both versions good compatibility each other well and can be easily used in combination.

Usage Tips:

  • Trigger words is not required.

  • Recommended model is AbyssOrangeMix3

  • Use a weight of 0.8 - 1.0

  • Use a Sampling steps of over 30

  • If you're not getting the intended result, try reviewing the values of 'Sampling steps' and 'Denoising strength'.

Tulpas are also called imaginary friends, and are fictitious beings created to protect their personalities.

Tulpas lose their voice or become invisible when they or their master reach adulthood.
